---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Jay Vergara — L&D strategist, cross-cultural communication specialist, and AI builder based in Tokyo.">
  <article class="max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-heading">Lead humanly. Learn constantly. Build with AI.</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-body leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm Jay Vergara. Originally from Vancouver, B.C. I've been living in Tokyo for over a decade now. Came thinking I'd stay a year or two and then... well, you know how that goes.
      </p>
      <p>
        I work in learning and development. Have for most of my career. Indeed, Rakuten, TELUS, Yellow Pages. Building training programs, leading L&D teams, trying to figure out why most corporate learning doesn't actually stick.
      </p>
      <p>
        These days I run <a href="https://peakpotentialconsulting.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">Peak Potential Consulting</a> with my business partner Matt Gates. We help companies build leaders, teams, and learning cultures that work across borders.
      </p>
      <p>
        I also can't stop thinking about AI. Not in the "robots are coming for your job" way. In the "this changes everything about how we develop people and I want to be figuring it out" way. I use AI every single day to run the business, write content, pursue my MBA at <a href="https://www.globis.ac.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">GLOBIS University</a>, and build systems I couldn't have built alone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-heading">What you'll find here</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-body leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-heading">Lead Humanly</strong> is the human side. Cross-cultural communication. Leadership development. Corporate learning strategy. The stuff I've spent my career figuring out, often by getting it wrong first.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong class="text-heading">Build with AI</strong> is the practical side. Tutorials, workflow breakdowns, honest takes on what AI can and can't do for people in HR, L&D, and leadership. Not theory. Things I've actually built and used.
      </p>
      <p>
        The thesis is simple. The leaders who will matter most in the next decade are deeply human AND technologically fluent. Not one or the other. Both.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-heading">The personal stuff</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-body leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm a dad. A watch collector (three slot collection, if you're curious). I write a separate blog called <a href="https://rugged-ivy-tokyo.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">Rugged Ivy Tokyo</a> about watches, heritage menswear, and living intentionally from Tokyo.
      </p>
      <p>
        I speak English natively and Japanese professionally. I'm pursuing an MBA not because I needed the credential but because I genuinely wanted to understand what I didn't know.
      </p>
      <p>
        I believe the best content comes from experience. Not expertise performed for an audience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-heading">Connect</h2>
    <div class="space-y-2 text-body leading-relaxed">
      <p>Best way to follow my work is on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/vergarajay/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-1 mt-3 text-sm">
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/vergarajay/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://peakpotentialconsulting.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors">Peak Potential Consulting</a>
        <a href="https://rugged-ivy-tokyo.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors">Rugged Ivy Tokyo</a>
        <a href="https://www.globis.ac.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors">GLOBIS University</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
